      "start_time": 114.93,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9bc8d78b-c060-4131-8855-db4277c30fdc",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "So we off roaded it to a spot like off of, like the Blm trail, attached the the hammocks to 2 separate trees, and on top of the on the roof rack."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
