      "order_number": 101,
      "text": "So I mean she's"
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 310.73,
      "start_time": 310.51,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 102,
      "text": "she."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 314.37,
      "start_time": 310.96,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 103,
      "text": "I mean she would survive for sure, just not very too much for she."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 316.37,
      "start_time": 314.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 104,
      "text": "I can't lift them up, or anything right now."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 319.27,
      "start_time": 316.71,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9bc8d78b-c060-4131-8855-db4277c30fdc",
      "order_number": 105,
      "text": "Totally makes makes way more sense for you to stay."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 319.95,
      "start_time": 319.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 106,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 321.84,
      "start_time": 320.16,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 107,
      "text": "I mean, she's actually the doctors right now."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 334.25,
      "start_time": 322.05,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 108,
      "text": "She's to go like every every week to make sure everything's good, but seems like the baby would be coming before that, and I'm supposed to take the kids to take into my parents house and on the East Coast to drop them off so like we don't have to worry about them whenever she has a baby."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 336.14,
      "start_time": 334.46,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 109,
      "text": "So I gotta do that like June sixth."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 339.78,
      "start_time": 337.39,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 110,
      "text": "So a lot of traveling back and forth, but."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 342.9,
      "start_time": 340.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9bc8d78b-c060-4131-8855-db4277c30fdc",
      "order_number": 111,
      "text": "Yeah, gotta do what you gotta do."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 344.41,
      "start_time": 343.59,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 112,
      "text": "Yeah, it's it'll be."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 347.29,
      "start_time": 344.62,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 113,
      "text": "It's gonna be hell for like 4 h flying with them by myself."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 348.72,
      "start_time": 347.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 114,
      "text": "But it won't be too bad."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 355.29,
      "start_time": 355.05,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9bc8d78b-c060-4131-8855-db4277c30fdc",
      "order_number": 115,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 358.88,
      "start_time": 355.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9bc8d78b-c060-4131-8855-db4277c30fdc",
      "order_number": 116,
      "text": "Once Drake confirms your denies, there's 2 dancers and give you some time back."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 361.75,
      "start_time": 361.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9bc8d78b-c060-4131-8855-db4277c30fdc",
      "order_number": 117,
      "text": "Thin."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 408.9,
      "start_time": 408.72,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 118,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 410.17,
      "start_time": 409.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 119,
      "text": "Drake sent me some notes earlier."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 413.6,
      "start_time": 410.35,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 120,
      "text": "I didn't read them until now, but it sounds like Guy wasn't super interested in taking the call."
    },
    {
      "id": "30382990-af80-4c03-9293-584e17c82512",
      "recording_id": "fec7aa44-d442-4adc-affe-de9341b291ea",
      "end_time": 418.38,
      "start_time": 417.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "4f214303-6068-4c33-b997-beba66e6b0c1",
      "order_number": 121,
      "text": "He said, that he's heard about it."
    },
